data.description: Fully remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bath in NW Palm Bay. NEW ROOF, NEW KITCHEN, NEW FLOORS and more From the front door to the shaded fenced backyard, there is so much to love in this house. You'll love cooking in the spacious kitchen with granite counters, soft close cabinets, and SO much storage! The updated bathrooms are spa-like and the whole house has fresh paint and new flooring. There is a screened porch to enjoy the Florida weather and an enclosed porch flooded with natural light perfect for so many things - office, playroom, dining area, family room. All this plus a 2 car garage and on a large lot. Come see it today.
